# Git Commit Messages

- **Format:** `type(scope): subject`
- **Types:** `feat`, `fix`, `docs`, `style`, `refactor`, `test`, `chore`
- **Examples:** `feat(sms): Add bulk SMS`, `fix(firebase): Resolve timeout`, `docs(03): Update manifest components`

See **docs/09-code-style.md** (Git Commit Messages).
